HEADWORD: Lifelike
<hw>Life"like`</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧f"l⟦imac⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. <er>Lively</er>.]</ety> <def>Like a living being; resembling
